Name: Average time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total time between SW-Initial Reviewer Selection and the first occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average duration of SW-Initial Reviewer Selection until the next distinct activity in each variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity SW-Initial Reviewer Selection and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to be followed by any reviewer-related activity (e.g., SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, SW-Reviewer Unavailable)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total elapsed time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision across variants that include both activities
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time between SW-Initial Reviewer Selection and SW-Reviewer Selection is now due in variants where deadlines are explicitly tracked
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due'

Name: Time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to the first Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Average cycle time of SW-Initial Reviewer Selection when followed by multiple rounds of SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Initial Reviewer Selection and SW-Reviewer No Response in cases where no reviewer accepts
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response'

Name: Total time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in variants that reach this stage
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Initial Reviewer Selection and the last reviewer assignment attempt before a reviewer agrees
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to SW-Reviewer Selection is 1 week late in delayed variants
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is 1 week late'

Name: Average duration between SW-Initial Reviewer Selection and the first occurrence of either SW-Reviewer Agreed or SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to the final disposition activity (e.g., SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Reject, SW-EIC Major Revision) grouped by outcome type
Metric: ERROR: computing metric {'begin': activity == 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection'", 'end': "activity in ['SW-EIC Accept', 'SW-EIC Reject', 'SW-EIC Major Revision', 'SW-EIC Minor Revision', 'SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit']", 'aggregation': 'average', 'group_by': 'concept:name'}"
